  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/924",
  "title": "numericRefinementList should be able to filter on multiple ranges",
  "body": "For example, I would like to be able to provide this:\n- [ ] < 500\n- [ ] 1499-5000\n- [ ] 5000+ \n\nAnd be able to select multiple ranges:\n- [x] < 500\n- [ ] 1499-5000\n- [x] 5000+ \n\nRight now, we only provide radio buttons by default because the default refinement option is to select only one range.\n\nBeing able to select multiple ranges could be nice, sometimes useful.\n",
